{
  "id": 5077600085082112,
  "name": "text-decoration-skip-ink: all",
  "summary": "Add support for the `all` value for the CSS text-decoration-skip-ink property, as specified in https://drafts.csswg.org/css-text-decor-4/#text-decoration-skip-ink-property.\n\nThe `text-decoration-skip-ink` property already supports `auto` and `none`. The `all` value extends this by unconditionally applying ink-skipping to all glyphs - including CJK characters - whereas `auto` leaves CJK characters un-skipped because ink-skipping tends to produce undesirable visual results for ideographic scripts at typical underline positions.\n\nWith `text-decoration-skip-ink: all`, authors who have adjusted `text-underline-position` or `text-underline-offset` to avoid clashing with CJK glyphs can explicitly opt in to ink-skipping for those characters as well.",
